    "title": "Process Engineer Vacancy at ACC Limited - 2026 Batch",
    "description": "We at ACC Limited are looking for an experienced Process Engineer based out of Nashik. If you are a result-oriented professional with a passion for excellence, we want to hear from you.\n\nAbout ACC Limited:\nACC Limited is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Prepare production cost analysis and efficiency reports\n• Conduct root cause analysis for quality rejections and defects\n• Ensure compliance with safety regulations and factory acts\n• Coordinate with design and engineering teams on product improvements\n• Maintain accurate production records and prepare daily reports\n• Monitor equipment performance and coordinate preventive maintenance\n• Ensure product quality meets internal and customer specifications\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Ed / M.Ed from a recognized institution\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Lean Manufacturing\n• Proficiency in AutoCAD\n• Proficiency in TPM\n• Proficiency in ERP Systems\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain Management\n• Proficiency in SolidWorks\n• Proficiency in PLC/SCADA\n• Proficiency in Project Management\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Referral bonus program\n• Learning & development budget\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Nashik, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with ACC Limited!",
